    {
      "id": "manifest-contract-root",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "📜 Manifest Contract (Normative)",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Manifest Contract\n\n**Authority:** Absolute\n\nEvery Twilite graph MUST contain exactly one Manifest node that conforms to this contract.\n\nGraphs without a valid Manifest are **not portable, not safe, and not executable**.\n\nIf a tool or agent does not understand the Manifest, it MUST refuse to act.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
