        "markdown": "## Identity (REQUIRED)\n\nDefines what this graph **is**.\n\n- graphId (immutable UUID v4)\n- name\n- version (semver)\n- description\n- createdAt\n- updatedAt\n\nTools may read identity but may only update `updatedAt`.",
