      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Intent & Scope (REQUIRED)\n\nDeclares how the graph is interpreted.\n\n- kind: graph | fragment | documentation | workflow | simulation | circuit | knowledge-map | contract | executable | other\n- scope: human | agent | tool | mixed\n\nEditors MUST NOT guess intent.\nAgents MUST respect it.\nUnknown kinds are opaque.",
        "_classBinding": {
