    {
      "id": "manifest-dependencies",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "4. Dependencies & Requirements",
      "position": {
        "x": 840,
        "y": 360
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Dependencies (REQUIRED)\n\nDeclares what must exist for validity.\n\n- nodeTypes\n- portContracts\n- skills\n- schemaVersions\n- optional\n\n**Skill dependencies are mandatory.**\n- If a node definition declares a skill, it **must** appear here.\n- Missing skills invalidate execution.\n\n**Version mismatches are warnings only (for now).**\n- Version conflicts MUST surface as warnings.\n- They MUST NOT block loading until a stricter policy is adopted.\n\nOptional dependencies must never be assumed.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
