    {
      "id": "manifest-authority",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "5. Authority & Mutation Policy",
      "position": {
        "x": -720,
        "y": 820
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 520,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Authority & Mutation Policy (REQUIRED)\n\nDefines what may change and by whom.\n\n- mutation rules\n- allowed actors\n- styleAuthority\n- history rules\n\nIf appendOnly = true, deletes are forbidden.\nHistory rules MUST be enforced.\n\n### Graph Boundary (Authority Scope)\n- `none`: load full file (no boundary)\n- `root`: load manifest-rooted subgraph (stop at other Manifests)\n- `cluster`: load only the cluster containing the Manifest node\n\n**Reachability rule (root boundary):**\n- Only structural edges extend authority: `contains` and legacy `child`\n- Cluster membership is structural for nodes in the same file/scope\n- All other edge types are **non-structural** and do not confer authority\n\n**Cluster constraint:**\n- Clusters must only reference local nodes\n- External node IDs are ignored and should warn",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
