      "width": 360,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Document Settings (OPTIONAL)\n\nSettings define the default presentation for a graph.\n\nStored in the Manifest as `data.settings`.\n\nIf omitted, renderers must fall back to their own defaults.\n\nFields may include:\n- theme (optional)\n- backgroundImage\n- defaultNodeColor / defaultEdgeColor\n- gridSize, snapToGrid\n- edgeRouting + layout\n- github settings\n- autoSave",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
